## ▶️ How to Run

```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/123AmAy/Image-captioning-model-CNN-LSTMS-/tree/main


# Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt

# To Train the model
   Run the 3_train.py
```

# To Test the model
   Run the test.py


